snippet.title: Fallout: Vault 13 - Shady Sands Showcase (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Fallout: Vault 13 is an upcoming modification for Fallout 4 that seeks to remake and reimagine Fallout 1 in Fallout 4's engine.

Fallout: Vault 13 - Shady Sands Showcase (With Commentary): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ibk6r8-sHO8
